text: Hybolasius genalis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Broun in 1903. It is known from New Zealand. It contains the varietas Hybolasius genalis var. tumidellus.BioLib.cz - Hybolasius genalis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1903
